      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey can u help me with a sentiment analysis project? i got these posts from a local community group regarding the new zoning and housing laws in the North End district. i need to know the general vibe and what they seem to be upset about.\n\n1. \"They're trying to push us out of our own neighborhood. we been here for generations and now they want to build luxury condos? no way.\"\n2. \"Every time they change the rules, it just makes it harder for families like mine to stay. it's not fair.\"\n3. \"the new rules are just gonna bring more noise and chaos to the streets. we dont want this.\"\n4. \"standard gentrification tactics. they ignore us then try to rebuild everything around us. we aren't going anywhere.\"\n\ncan u summarize the sentiment and what the underlying reasoning for the community's reaction is?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
